ve the timberline, in addition to the exclusively mountainous distribution, indicate that the species is indeed alpine, showing a pattern similar to other highly mobile vertebrates restricted to mountain areas and absent from flatlands. Nevertheless, its apparent elevational distribution may still be biased toward lower areas, due to the scarcity of surveys in high mountain habitats.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Alberdi, Antton", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Garin, Inazio", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Aizpurua, Ostaizka", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Aihartza, Joxerra", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/de93624b00a476ab10f5c1cad0435943", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/aa81933b753f1b56f40875c6dbbc9af265f2d14e1b25fd5afe9b16c4a9253008", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/G3IIIHVT", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/G3IIIHVT", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/957200592e7fd9c14fa9bbb4f24ff3fa!/b122125-124686", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "2", "pages": "451-461", "title": "Acta Chiropterologica", "volume": "15"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/de93624b00a476ab10f5c1cad0435943"}, {